                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for producing hydrogen by directly electrolyzing seawater through full spectrum of solar energy",
                    "一种利用太阳能全光谱直接电解海水制氢装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a device and a method for directly electrolyzing seawater to produce hydrogen by using a solar full spectrum. The system is composed of a solar full spectrum utilization device, a solar cell panel, a microporous hydrophobic membrane, a support frame, an aluminum plate, a hydrogen breather pipe, a gas-liquid separation pipe, a strong brine discharge pipe and the like. The solar full-spectrum utilization device performs photovoltaic and photo-thermal utilization on sunlight, photovoltaic energy is absorbed by the monocrystalline silicon solar cell panel to generate power and input into the electrolytic cell, and hydrogen and oxygen are generated through electrolysis. Photo-thermal energy is transmitted to seawater in the seawater annular pipeline through the solar full-spectrum utilization device shell, water vapor generated by evaporation of hot seawater penetrates through the microporous hydrophobic membrane, condensation on the surface of the aluminum plate is accelerated under the action of hydrogen serving as light gas, latent heat of condensation is absorbed by seawater of the next stage, evaporation and condensation of the seawater are promoted, and energy is saved. Multi-stage fresh water output is achieved through multi-stage design, in addition, photovoltaic waste heat and seawater waste heat are recycled through heat transfer, energy loss is reduced, and the energy utilization rate of the system is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种利用太阳能全光谱直接电解海水制氢装置及方法，该系统由太阳能全光谱利用装置、太阳能电池板、微孔疏水膜、支撑架、铝板、氢气通气管、气液分离管、浓盐水排出管等部分组成；太阳能全光谱利用装置对太阳光进行光伏光热分别利用，光伏能量被单晶硅太阳能电池板吸收发电并输入到电解槽，电解产生氢气与氧气；光热能量通过太阳能全光谱利用装置外壳传输到海水环形管道的海水中，热海水蒸发产生的水蒸气透过微孔疏水膜，在氢气作为轻质气体的作用下，加快在铝板表面冷凝，冷凝潜热被下一级海水吸收并促进其蒸发冷凝，经过多级设计实现多级淡水产出，另外利用热传递对光伏余热和海水余热进行回收，减少能量损失，提高系统能量利用率。"
                }
            ]
